      <scopecontent>
         
         
         <head>Collection Overview</head>
         
         
         <p>Collection contains deeds, plats, account books, regimental papers of North Carolina troops in the Civil War, and a scrapbook of letters and clippings regarding Capehart's death on January 5, 1899.
         </p>
      
      
